WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 12=

01:50.950 --> 01:51.800
Hurry.

01:51.820 --> 01:52.730
- Do it.
- Hurry.

01:53.110 --> 01:54.140
- Kill her.
- Hurry.

01:54.140 --> 01:54.990
Kill her.

01:55.470 --> 01:56.750
Kill her now.

01:57.190 --> 02:00.230
Kill her.

02:00.500 --> 02:02.030
Don't you want to go to war?

02:02.750 --> 02:04.470
Kill her and you can go.

02:05.030 --> 02:06.580
Be quick.

02:06.580 --> 02:08.790
Kill her.

02:08.790 --> 02:10.300
Kill her now!

02:10.300 --> 02:12.550
- Do it now!
- Hurry!

02:12.550 --> 02:14.020
- Do it now!
- Kill her!

02:14.020 --> 02:14.950
Kill her!

02:16.990 --> 02:18.620
Kill her now!

02:18.620 --> 02:19.900
Kill her!

02:20.560 --> 02:21.420
Kill her!

02:21.420 --> 02:22.260
Do it now!

02:36.420 --> 02:37.260
You...

02:38.990 --> 02:39.830
I knew it.

02:40.460 --> 02:42.070
You aren't the real Xiaoxiao.

02:42.510 --> 02:44.270
Xiaoxiao is a nice person.

02:44.740 --> 02:46.390
She would never make me kill anyone!

02:49.860 --> 02:51.230
You're the real Xiaoxiao.

02:52.270 --> 02:53.110
Take it back.

03:04.270 --> 03:05.300
Very well.

03:10.270 --> 03:11.900
Since you refuse to kill her,

03:13.350 --> 03:15.620
you'll die with her!

04:06.530 --> 04:07.390
Captain Han,

04:07.390 --> 04:08.230
you go on scouting.

04:08.510 --> 04:09.790
Qingsheng and I
will join you in three days.

04:10.060 --> 04:10.910
Yes, General.

04:10.910 --> 04:12.460
Qingsheng, we're going back to Shuozhou.

04:12.790 --> 04:13.630
- Let's go.
- Yes.

04:55.110 --> 04:56.470
Why did you protect me?

04:57.860 --> 04:58.990
You may die.

05:00.380 --> 05:01.620
But I can never die.

05:03.590 --> 05:05.260
I just feel pain.

05:13.820 --> 05:15.820
Xiaoxiao, please don't die.

05:16.860 --> 05:19.620
I... I promise I'll grow stronger.

05:20.620 --> 05:21.860
The General said

05:22.060 --> 05:23.550
those who always protect others

05:24.110 --> 05:25.470
are very lonely.

05:26.110 --> 05:28.060
The General and I

05:28.060 --> 05:29.710
will protect you together

05:30.110 --> 05:31.940
just like how you protected us.

05:32.670 --> 05:33.510
All right?

05:34.990 --> 05:36.940
Xiaoxiao, please don't die.

05:43.420 --> 05:44.380
Take it.

05:45.300 --> 05:46.140
With this,

05:46.420 --> 05:47.910
no spirit can ever hurt you.

05:49.500 --> 05:50.550
Go find Meng Wan.

05:51.550 --> 05:52.940
Don't get in my way here.

06:08.380 --> 06:09.220
You...

06:10.380 --> 06:11.740
- He...
- He has the Lantern.

06:11.740 --> 06:12.580
I can't hurt him.

06:13.740 --> 06:14.580
You go after him.

06:15.230 --> 06:17.030
But I... I...

06:17.380 --> 06:18.740
Go after him.

06:20.030 --> 06:21.910
Or I will kill you now.

06:23.180 --> 06:24.020
Fine.

06:24.180 --> 06:25.020
All right.

06:25.260 --> 06:26.260
I...

06:26.420 --> 06:27.470
I'll... I'll go after him.

06:51.670 --> 06:52.590
You just gave that boy

06:52.590 --> 06:53.990
the Spirits Lantern?

06:55.500 --> 06:56.910
What if it gets him killed?

07:03.550 --> 07:04.390
Chenying...

07:05.820 --> 07:07.300
He's no worse than any of you.

07:13.500 --> 07:14.420
Before the sun rises

07:14.420 --> 07:15.990
when I get back my power,

07:16.670 --> 07:17.820
if you still can't find

07:17.820 --> 07:18.670
my vital center,

07:19.060 --> 07:20.990
prepare to vanish.

07:26.910 --> 07:27.750
Fang Chang,

07:30.060 --> 07:31.150
take off this guise.

07:45.180 --> 07:47.670
So you knew it was me,

07:48.990 --> 07:49.910
Your Grace.

07:53.990 --> 07:56.260
Without your obsession
with being a mortal,

07:57.230 --> 08:00.030
I wouldn't have this great opportunity.

08:01.120 --> 08:01.990
After I knew

08:01.990 --> 08:03.910
you were controlling that woman,

08:04.740 --> 08:06.710
I kept watching secretly

08:08.110 --> 08:10.910
until you abandoned her body.

08:18.060 --> 08:19.110
Stay back!

08:21.110 --> 08:22.860
I found her.

08:33.070 --> 08:35.830
With your lingering power in her body,

08:35.990 --> 08:37.830
I took your form

08:38.950 --> 08:40.540
and manipulated her.

09:01.780 --> 09:04.020
When you have no spirit power,

09:05.860 --> 09:07.020
I'll kill you

09:07.900 --> 09:09.540
to avenge Yinyin.

09:13.950 --> 09:15.140
I've sensed your aura

09:15.140 --> 09:16.070
all along.

09:16.570 --> 09:17.430
I was just wondering

09:17.430 --> 09:18.280
what kind of trick

09:18.280 --> 09:19.310
you were going to play.

09:20.350 --> 09:21.470
I never thought

09:22.230 --> 09:23.620
it could be so boring.

09:25.070 --> 09:26.500
As for Shao Yinyin...

09:27.310 --> 09:28.830
She violated the Golden-wall Decrees

09:28.830 --> 09:29.950
and reaped what she sowed.

09:30.780 --> 09:32.230
She was your lover.

09:33.020 --> 09:34.660
To secure your position as Vice Lord,

09:34.660 --> 09:35.860
you killed her yourself.

09:36.260 --> 09:38.140
But now you seek revenge on me.

09:38.620 --> 09:39.780
Isn't that ridiculous?

09:40.430 --> 09:41.500
Shut up!

10:19.500 --> 10:20.350
Fang Chang,

10:21.860 --> 10:23.470
you've lived for centuries.

10:24.350 --> 10:25.990
Is this all you've got?

10:28.140 --> 10:29.140
He Simu!

10:29.990 --> 10:31.900
To uphold the Golden-wall Decrees

10:31.900 --> 10:32.860
and protect mortals,

10:33.070 --> 10:34.740
you prey on spirits, your own kind!

10:36.470 --> 10:37.500
So today,

10:39.430 --> 10:40.590
I'll make you die

10:40.590 --> 10:43.070
at the hands of the mortals
under your protection.

11:12.950 --> 11:14.110
I didn't know

11:15.110 --> 11:17.020
you could do the Puppet Technique.

11:18.990 --> 11:20.990
Die, He Simu!

11:38.020 --> 11:39.140
Stop!

11:40.710 --> 11:41.550
Don't run!

11:41.950 --> 11:42.830
Stop right there!

11:44.740 --> 11:45.580
Stop!

11:46.380 --> 11:47.990
If I catch you, I'll get rude!

11:50.430 --> 11:51.270
Stop!

11:52.140 --> 11:53.110
Stop right there!

11:54.950 --> 11:56.660
If I catch you, I'll show no mercy!

12:05.740 --> 12:06.580
Keep running.

12:06.830 --> 12:07.670
Try if you can.

12:10.950 --> 12:11.790
Boy,

12:13.500 --> 12:14.830
give me the jade pendant.

12:15.380 --> 12:16.990
After I kill that woman,

12:17.470 --> 12:19.710
I can give you some money.

12:27.540 --> 12:28.380
Give it to me.

12:28.780 --> 12:29.620
You wish!

12:30.310 --> 12:31.860
It belongs to Xiaoxiao.

12:32.380 --> 12:33.780
I won't give it to you unless I die!

12:34.540 --> 12:35.540
You little brat.

12:36.540 --> 12:37.740
We aren't enemies.

12:37.900 --> 12:38.780
But today,

12:38.990 --> 12:41.590
one of us has to die.

12:42.260 --> 12:43.900
Don't blame me.

12:51.950 --> 12:53.140
Who? Who did that?

12:53.310 --> 12:54.470
Who?

12:55.260 --> 12:56.100
Chenying.

12:56.740 --> 12:57.580
General.

13:02.470 --> 13:03.620
Who are you?

13:05.660 --> 13:06.500
You...

13:07.070 --> 13:08.830
Who... Who are you?

13:12.710 --> 13:13.620
You hurt him?

13:13.880 --> 13:14.720
So what?

13:14.740 --> 13:15.740
Want a fight?

13:35.190 --> 13:36.030
General,

13:36.660 --> 13:37.660
Xiaoxiao...

13:39.500 --> 13:40.540
Xiaoxiao...

13:45.230 --> 13:46.140
She...

13:46.140 --> 13:46.980
Clean up the mess.

13:49.310 --> 13:50.150
Are you all right?

14:01.230 --> 14:02.590
Without the puppets,

14:03.050 --> 14:03.900
can you not even

14:03.910 --> 14:05.540
find my vital center?

14:07.310 --> 14:08.540
Don't talk tough.

14:08.830 --> 14:10.310
When I make the puppets

14:10.310 --> 14:12.230
pierce you all over,

14:13.470 --> 14:15.430
I'll find your vital center.

14:26.830 --> 14:28.020
(My sense of touch is back.)

15:32.340 --> 15:37.430
♪Spirits are intoxicated♪

15:37.430 --> 15:41.580
♪With obsessions♪

15:43.880 --> 15:48.960
♪Forget the form to achieve♪

15:48.960 --> 15:53.120
♪Yet I can't♪

15:55.450 --> 15:59.100
♪Today, a home is granted♪

15:59.190 --> 16:00.380
Got any more moves?

16:01.140 --> 16:02.430
Bring them on.

16:02.740 --> 16:03.580
Stay back.

16:08.950 --> 16:10.140
Or I'll kill her.

16:13.230 --> 16:14.710
She's no threat to me.

16:15.990 --> 16:17.190
Say something else.

16:19.350 --> 16:20.540
Why don't you tell me

16:21.860 --> 16:22.990
where you managed to learn

16:22.990 --> 16:24.230
the Puppet Technique?

16:26.710 --> 16:27.860
You'll never know,

16:28.380 --> 16:29.470
He Simu.

17:03.140 --> 17:03.980
Simu.

17:04.630 --> 17:05.470
Simu.

17:06.300 --> 17:07.140
Simu.

17:17.740 --> 17:19.340
So this is how much it hurts

17:20.390 --> 17:21.340
when you're injured.

17:51.950 --> 17:53.100
I didn't lend you this sense

17:55.230 --> 17:56.710
to make you feel pain.

17:59.820 --> 18:01.500
It doesn't hurt anymore.

18:05.190 --> 18:06.260
Calm down,

18:06.710 --> 18:07.550
young general.

18:13.190 --> 18:14.390
I'm calm enough.

18:51.430 --> 18:53.150
I cleaned you
with three buckets of water.

18:53.500 --> 18:54.740
Luckily, you aren't a mortal.

18:55.150 --> 18:56.630
Or you would have bled out.

19:02.910 --> 19:03.750
Meng Wan.

19:22.300 --> 19:23.300
How do you feel?

19:24.990 --> 19:26.190
Is anything hurting?

19:27.300 --> 19:28.140
Feel?

19:29.630 --> 19:30.670
I can't feel anything.

19:32.580 --> 19:33.430
Soon, these wounds

19:33.430 --> 19:34.540
will heal on their own.

19:35.020 --> 19:35.860
A spirit

19:35.870 --> 19:36.740
heals quickly.

19:37.390 --> 19:38.230
Besides,

19:38.780 --> 19:39.780
I'm the Sovereign.

19:40.340 --> 19:41.340
I never die.

19:59.150 --> 20:00.060
General Duan,

20:00.910 --> 20:01.950
isn't it very rude

20:02.100 --> 20:03.260
when a mortal like you

20:03.990 --> 20:05.060
stares at a lady like this?

20:08.430 --> 20:09.540
What on earth happened?

20:15.870 --> 20:16.710
The mortal

20:16.710 --> 20:18.150
I used to possess

20:19.060 --> 20:19.910
is Qiao Yan.

20:21.710 --> 20:22.780
Before dying of illness,

20:22.780 --> 20:23.990
her mother made a deal with me

20:24.190 --> 20:25.030
that I'd protect her.

20:25.990 --> 20:27.190
So, I kept her by my side

20:27.500 --> 20:29.150
and nurtured her
with aura of my lantern.

20:30.150 --> 20:31.020
Later, her health

20:31.020 --> 20:31.910
improved a little.

20:32.630 --> 20:33.500
Besides,

20:33.500 --> 20:34.580
during the spell of senses,

20:34.580 --> 20:35.990
my own body was needed.

20:36.780 --> 20:37.620
So,

20:37.630 --> 20:38.580
I let her leave.

20:39.580 --> 20:40.630
You protected her.

20:41.820 --> 20:42.820
Why did she hurt you?

20:47.020 --> 20:48.740
She was just being manipulated.

20:51.580 --> 20:52.540
In Shanling Temple,

20:53.580 --> 20:54.910
someone called Fang Chang

20:56.390 --> 20:58.100
hated me for killing her lover.

20:58.430 --> 21:00.100
So when I didn't have power,

21:00.470 --> 21:01.870
he manipulated Qiao Yan's body

21:02.230 --> 21:03.150
and did such a thing.

21:07.950 --> 21:08.870
How is Miss He?

21:09.230 --> 21:10.630
Her wounds are healing quickly.

21:10.630 --> 21:11.470
She'll be fine.

21:12.340 --> 21:13.430
What a surprise.

21:13.710 --> 21:15.870
So Miss He really is a spirit.

21:16.260 --> 21:18.430
Her identity doesn't matter.

21:18.870 --> 21:19.710
I just know

21:19.910 --> 21:21.150
she did a great service to us.

21:23.470 --> 21:24.310
That makes sense.

21:25.100 --> 21:26.710
Without her,

21:26.710 --> 21:28.430
we wouldn't have taken Shuozhou.

21:28.910 --> 21:29.750
Miss He.

21:30.300 --> 21:31.150
She's a good spirit.

21:31.780 --> 21:32.620
She really is.

21:35.820 --> 21:37.390
Well, I'm quite curious.

21:40.430 --> 21:41.300
How did he know

21:41.300 --> 21:42.630
I lost my power?

21:43.470 --> 21:44.990
You didn't tell him, did you?

21:48.430 --> 21:49.270
You suspect me?

21:59.500 --> 22:00.470
I swear to you

22:03.020 --> 22:03.860
by my past,

22:05.100 --> 22:05.940
my future,

22:07.230 --> 22:08.950
my body, my heart,

22:09.390 --> 22:10.230
my family,

22:11.470 --> 22:12.780
my dream,

22:12.780 --> 22:14.100
my name,

22:14.100 --> 22:15.020
and everything I have,

22:16.300 --> 22:17.430
I will never

22:19.260 --> 22:20.100
ever

22:21.500 --> 22:22.670
do anything to hurt you

22:22.670 --> 22:23.580
even if I die.

22:40.710 --> 22:41.870
You can just deny it.

22:42.430 --> 22:43.870
Why are you overreacting so much?

22:48.260 --> 22:49.190
Oh, you're angry.

22:52.470 --> 22:54.150
I've never seen you angry before.

22:56.020 --> 22:57.580
Marshal Qin exiled you to the north,

22:58.260 --> 22:59.630
Wu Shengliu questioned you,

23:00.100 --> 23:01.470
and Qin's soldiers isolated you,

23:01.470 --> 23:02.500
but you were never angry.

23:03.150 --> 23:03.990
Now you're angry

23:03.990 --> 23:05.340
over such an ordinary question.

23:06.740 --> 23:07.950
Funny, indeed.

23:15.340 --> 23:16.300
But this time,

23:18.150 --> 23:19.630
I experienced what felt like dying.

23:22.230 --> 23:23.470
I felt this pain

23:23.470 --> 23:24.670
to its very limit.

23:27.670 --> 23:28.630
Getting this sense

23:29.150 --> 23:29.990
is worth it.

23:33.780 --> 23:35.100
Only someone who never dies

23:35.820 --> 23:37.390
would say something so arrogant.

23:39.500 --> 23:41.580
When I saw fresh and old wounds on you,

23:42.300 --> 23:44.060
I never felt anything.

23:45.060 --> 23:46.190
But since I've experienced

23:46.190 --> 23:47.740
such wounds,

23:48.630 --> 23:50.190
it breaks my heart to see you like this.

23:53.740 --> 23:55.340
Mortals like you

23:56.710 --> 23:58.020
are really fragile.

24:00.300 --> 24:01.820
If only I had found you

24:01.820 --> 24:03.230
when you joined the All-Knowing.

24:04.710 --> 24:05.550
In that case,

24:06.060 --> 24:07.580
you would have had fewer wounds

24:08.430 --> 24:09.470
and less pain.

24:15.820 --> 24:16.660
No.

24:19.020 --> 24:20.340
If you had met me at that time,

24:22.230 --> 24:23.580
you wouldn't have been interested.

24:25.060 --> 24:25.910
Now I've met you.

24:28.260 --> 24:29.100
I think

24:30.260 --> 24:31.430
it's the perfect time.

24:37.060 --> 24:38.670
You don't want me to save you earlier?

24:39.780 --> 24:40.620
No.

24:41.990 --> 24:43.150
Back in the All-Knowing,

24:44.820 --> 24:45.950
I was in pain and confused.

24:47.190 --> 24:48.260
And I was always fearful.

24:50.870 --> 24:51.990
My soul was a crucible.

24:53.580 --> 24:55.150
There was no room for love.

24:57.390 --> 24:58.990
I'm glad that you see me as I am now.

25:01.670 --> 25:03.230
Now I'm clear-minded

25:05.150 --> 25:06.060
and resolute.

25:07.150 --> 25:07.990
I need no redemption.

25:09.150 --> 25:09.990
I'd rather fall,

25:11.710 --> 25:12.550
survive rough times,

25:14.020 --> 25:15.470
rebuild my body, reshape my soul,

25:16.710 --> 25:17.630
and get worldly-wise,

25:19.740 --> 25:20.580
in exchange for...

25:21.080 --> 25:23.480
♪Miracles, eternity, and radiance♪

25:23.500 --> 25:24.340
Meeting you again.

25:24.340 --> 25:26.640
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

25:26.640 --> 25:29.050
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

25:29.050 --> 25:33.200
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

25:39.430 --> 25:40.820
I just asked casually.

25:41.470 --> 25:42.670
Don't be so serious.

25:43.500 --> 25:44.740
This is how I honestly feel.

25:49.190 --> 25:50.630
My heart only holds evil thoughts

25:51.150 --> 25:52.100
instead of true love.

25:53.500 --> 25:54.910
Say that to someone else.

25:55.730 --> 25:58.450
♪A dream I'm lost in♪

25:59.080 --> 26:00.390
♪If I could kiss your hand♪

26:01.060 --> 26:01.900
I've recovered.

26:02.090 --> 26:05.300
♪I'd bear your feelings♪

26:05.760 --> 26:06.890
♪Thanks to fate♪

26:06.890 --> 26:08.520
♪I'm blessed to have met you♪

26:08.520 --> 26:11.230
♪Then I won't let you go♪

26:11.470 --> 26:13.720
♪I wish I could be a firework♪

26:13.720 --> 26:17.840
♪To burn out for the moment you turn♪

26:35.580 --> 26:36.430
(Since you've come,)

26:38.140 --> 26:38.990
(don't expect)

26:38.990 --> 26:40.780
(to disappear from my life.)

26:52.740 --> 26:54.390
Help me, Your Lordship!

26:54.710 --> 26:56.470
Help me!

26:58.430 --> 26:59.390
Your Lordship.

26:59.390 --> 27:01.540
What makes you so flustered?

27:02.430 --> 27:04.870
I'm too old

27:05.190 --> 27:06.580
to hear or see well.

27:06.950 --> 27:09.630
So I entrusted Fang Chang

27:09.910 --> 27:11.500
with all the affairs of my branch.

27:12.020 --> 27:12.910
I never thought

27:13.060 --> 27:15.390
he could do something so terrible

27:15.580 --> 27:17.710
in the Mortal World.

27:17.990 --> 27:20.340
He manipulated some mortals

27:20.580 --> 27:22.500
to assassinate Her Grace.

27:24.100 --> 27:25.190
The older you grow,

27:25.190 --> 27:26.820
the more cowardly you get.

27:27.500 --> 27:29.020
Since Her Grace took the throne,

27:29.020 --> 27:30.020
being assassinated

27:30.390 --> 27:31.820
has been like a daily occurrence.

27:33.150 --> 27:34.910
Not this time.

27:35.780 --> 27:36.710
I don't know

27:36.710 --> 27:38.500
how Fang Chang did that,

27:38.740 --> 27:40.580
but he severely wounded her.

27:41.390 --> 27:42.910
She was injured

27:42.910 --> 27:44.710
from head to toe.

28:13.100 --> 28:14.070
- Chenying.
- General.

28:14.950 --> 28:15.820
- Awake?
- General.

28:15.820 --> 28:17.020
How is Xiaoxiao?

28:18.060 --> 28:18.900
Don't worry.

28:19.060 --> 28:19.990
She's fine.

28:19.990 --> 28:21.020
But General,

28:21.500 --> 28:22.430
that imposter

28:22.430 --> 28:24.100
pierced through Xiaoxiao's body.

28:24.340 --> 28:26.060
She bled a lot.

28:26.540 --> 28:27.580
Is she really fine?

28:27.710 --> 28:28.820
She must be in pain.

28:32.740 --> 28:33.580
It's true.

28:34.230 --> 28:35.910
She's formidable.

28:36.780 --> 28:37.670
She's the Sovereign.

28:38.060 --> 28:39.190
Nothing can harm her.

28:40.150 --> 28:42.230
She's resting now.

28:43.020 --> 28:44.150
You can have something to eat

28:44.500 --> 28:45.740
and see her when she wakes up.

28:48.260 --> 28:49.340
Sovereign?

28:50.990 --> 28:53.100
Xiaoxiao told me

28:53.910 --> 28:55.780
the Sovereign is the head of spirits

28:55.780 --> 28:56.620
with great power.

28:56.870 --> 28:57.710
That's right.

29:14.230 --> 29:15.070
General,

29:15.740 --> 29:16.670
I've made up my mind.

29:16.670 --> 29:17.510
I must grow stronger.

29:17.950 --> 29:19.430
I'll learn martial arts from you.

29:19.780 --> 29:21.580
I will protect both of you

29:21.580 --> 29:22.710
so that you won't get hurt

29:22.910 --> 29:24.150
and you can do greater things.

29:26.470 --> 29:27.740
But I remember you wished

29:28.060 --> 29:29.340
to eat eight pancakes at a time.

29:29.780 --> 29:30.780
With meat filling.

29:37.100 --> 29:38.990
I don't want pancakes anymore.

29:39.190 --> 29:40.060
I...

29:40.060 --> 29:41.670
I wouldn't wind

29:41.670 --> 29:42.630
eating no more pancakes.

29:43.300 --> 29:44.500
All I want is to protect you.

29:45.060 --> 29:46.500
This will be my only wish.

29:54.060 --> 29:54.900
All right.

29:56.300 --> 29:57.340
I'll make you stronger.

30:08.950 --> 30:09.790
What's wrong?

30:13.780 --> 30:14.630
General,

30:16.990 --> 30:19.430
if Xiaoxiao is a spirit,

30:21.580 --> 30:22.710
does it mean she can't

30:22.710 --> 30:23.740
stay with us forever?

30:24.740 --> 30:26.230
Will she leave us?

30:33.820 --> 30:34.660
General,

30:35.340 --> 30:36.300
Xiaoxiao...

30:36.430 --> 30:38.100
She... She really likes you.

30:38.260 --> 30:39.100
Because of you,

30:39.260 --> 30:41.020
she's been lovesick.

30:41.430 --> 30:43.100
Don't... Don't you like her?

30:43.740 --> 30:45.540
If you have feelings for each other,

30:45.780 --> 30:46.910
she will stay.

30:47.740 --> 30:48.580
Lovesick?

30:49.470 --> 30:50.310
She said that?

30:54.420 --> 30:55.260
She says anything

30:55.260 --> 30:56.470
that comes to mind.

31:01.230 --> 31:02.070
Chenying,

31:02.710 --> 31:03.820
I'll tell you something.

31:05.260 --> 31:06.430
Can you keep it to yourself?

31:08.190 --> 31:09.050
Yes.

31:09.060 --> 31:10.580
I won't tell anyone.

31:11.190 --> 31:12.030
All right.

31:13.260 --> 31:14.100
Xiaoxiao often says

31:14.110 --> 31:15.300
she likes me

31:15.990 --> 31:16.830
or adores me,

31:17.740 --> 31:18.710
but that's all fake.

31:19.470 --> 31:20.870
She doesn't like me at all.

31:21.710 --> 31:23.910
Those are just jokes.

31:26.500 --> 31:27.390
To her,

31:28.630 --> 31:30.470
I'm merely a special mortal.

31:31.820 --> 31:32.670
I'm special enough

31:33.820 --> 31:35.100
to make her forgive my offense.

31:35.740 --> 31:36.820
But I'm not special enough

31:37.540 --> 31:38.390
to make her love me.

31:44.340 --> 31:45.190
I've never said

31:45.190 --> 31:46.100
that I like her.

31:47.630 --> 31:48.470
Actually,

31:50.150 --> 31:51.150
I really like her.

31:54.740 --> 31:55.580
Really.

31:58.670 --> 32:00.430
Are... Are you sure?

32:02.430 --> 32:03.300
You promised me

32:03.710 --> 32:04.780
you'd keep this secret.

32:05.500 --> 32:06.740
You must not tell her.

32:06.740 --> 32:08.300
I... I won't tell her.

32:08.710 --> 32:09.670
Then General,

32:09.670 --> 32:10.510
let's try together

32:10.520 --> 32:11.470
to make her stay.

32:11.470 --> 32:12.310
Shall we?

32:13.230 --> 32:14.100
We'll make her stay.

32:16.870 --> 32:17.710
Eat up.

32:21.990 --> 32:22.830
Xu,

32:23.100 --> 32:24.500
Commandant Xia is ready.

32:24.500 --> 32:25.630
You can leave anytime.

32:27.300 --> 32:28.190
Watch over Mingfeng.

32:28.950 --> 32:30.540
Take care of the manipulated citizens.

32:30.780 --> 32:31.780
Keep this under wraps.

32:32.710 --> 32:33.550
Wait until I'm back.

32:35.950 --> 32:36.820
Take care of Xiaoxiao.

32:42.540 --> 32:47.860
(Yiyuan Courtyard)

32:59.740 --> 33:00.580
Great Ancestor,

33:00.990 --> 33:02.820
you've finally summoned me.

33:03.670 --> 33:04.510
Tell me.

33:05.150 --> 33:07.190
What does it feel like to have senses?

33:07.580 --> 33:09.390
Which sense did you have this time?

33:13.100 --> 33:13.940
Fengyi,

33:15.340 --> 33:16.340
I experienced

33:16.340 --> 33:17.430
what death felt like.

33:20.820 --> 33:21.910
I had the sense of touch.

33:22.190 --> 33:23.030
When I lost my power,

33:23.300 --> 33:24.710
some evil spirits knew about it

33:24.710 --> 33:25.710
and tried to kill me.

33:26.100 --> 33:27.020
It was really fun.

33:28.340 --> 33:29.190
Having a sense

33:29.190 --> 33:30.670
will make you lose all your power?

33:31.540 --> 33:32.380
Then Great Ancestor,

33:32.480 --> 33:33.340
will you continue

33:33.340 --> 33:34.740
to get other senses?

33:35.580 --> 33:36.430
Why wouldn't I?

33:37.340 --> 33:38.870
It's a rare opportunity.

33:40.190 --> 33:41.340
And the time

33:41.780 --> 33:43.260
when I had the sense of touch

33:44.260 --> 33:46.020
left a deep impression on me.

33:48.500 --> 33:49.470
And thankfully,

33:49.950 --> 33:50.950
those brainless fools

33:50.950 --> 33:52.780
added to the fun.

33:54.150 --> 33:55.020
Great Ancestor,

33:55.300 --> 33:56.180
it seems

33:56.190 --> 33:57.740
you've been away for so long

33:57.740 --> 33:58.740
that you can't suppress

33:58.740 --> 33:59.990
those ambitious spirits.

34:00.150 --> 34:01.340
I've never suppressed them.

34:02.010 --> 34:02.860
I've just killed them,

34:02.870 --> 34:04.190
haven't I?

34:06.580 --> 34:08.270
They have to bow to me

34:08.990 --> 34:10.430
unless they defeat me.

34:11.790 --> 34:13.060
I just never thought

34:13.700 --> 34:14.870
Song Xingyu was behind this,

34:14.870 --> 34:16.020
as the long-lost lord

34:16.020 --> 34:17.390
of Jiling Temple.

34:18.540 --> 34:19.540
What exactly happened?

34:20.830 --> 34:22.580
Fang Chang from Shanling Temple

34:22.580 --> 34:23.700
colluded with Song Xingyu

34:24.310 --> 34:25.580
and learned his unique skill,

34:25.580 --> 34:26.990
the Puppet Technique.

34:27.870 --> 34:29.500
When I lost my power,

34:30.500 --> 34:31.390
Fang Chang set up

34:31.390 --> 34:32.350
that clumsy trap.

34:35.620 --> 34:36.700
Song Xingyu has hidden

34:36.700 --> 34:38.140
in the Mortal World for so long

34:38.140 --> 34:39.310
without being caught.

34:39.950 --> 34:41.700
As master of the Starhaven Sect,

34:42.220 --> 34:43.660
aren't you being irresponsible?

34:46.160 --> 34:47.020
Spirits like you

34:47.020 --> 34:47.950
didn't catch him either.

34:52.870 --> 34:53.790
Sorry, Great Ancestor.

34:54.180 --> 34:55.750
I'll widen the search scope immediately.

34:55.910 --> 34:57.180
Once we get news of Song Xingyu,

34:57.350 --> 34:58.470
I'll let you know.

35:42.310 --> 35:43.150
Confess.

35:44.660 --> 35:46.350
How did you wound Her Grace?

35:46.540 --> 35:49.990
A lot of spirits want to kill He Simu.

35:51.060 --> 35:52.100
This time,

35:52.700 --> 35:54.700
I waited until she lost her power.

35:54.700 --> 35:56.470
I shouldn't miss that chance.

35:59.100 --> 36:00.180
Do you know

36:00.750 --> 36:01.660
how great it felt

36:01.660 --> 36:03.500
when I was torturing

36:03.500 --> 36:04.470
our sovereign?

36:14.140 --> 36:15.430
The bright red blood

36:15.910 --> 36:17.180
kept streaming down!

36:17.390 --> 36:18.950
She was trembling all over with pain!

36:21.100 --> 36:23.100
Though she was the Sovereign,

36:23.500 --> 36:25.700
she lost her power and felt the pain.

36:27.540 --> 36:29.350
I really should have let you see

36:29.700 --> 36:31.540
how she looked as she was dying.

36:32.020 --> 36:34.700
She was truly pitiful.

36:48.990 --> 36:50.430
Who conspired with you?

36:58.580 --> 36:59.990
Your death is upon you.

37:00.620 --> 37:01.700
No point in hiding it!

37:02.390 --> 37:04.180
I'm going to die,

37:04.500 --> 37:06.580
whether I confess or not.

37:10.100 --> 37:11.060
Yan Ke,

37:12.750 --> 37:15.180
you're just He Simu's lapdog!

37:23.180 --> 37:24.060
Yan Ke,

37:24.470 --> 37:25.790
you humble yourself

37:25.790 --> 37:27.540
and obey her completely, and then?

37:28.870 --> 37:29.990
She goes through men

37:29.990 --> 37:31.270
one after another.

37:31.430 --> 37:33.100
But you'll never be chosen!

37:43.700 --> 37:50.260
(Yiyuan Courtyard)

37:50.580 --> 37:51.420
Yan,

37:51.870 --> 37:52.710
there you are.

37:54.950 --> 37:55.790
Simu.

37:56.220 --> 37:57.060
You're going out?

37:57.500 --> 37:58.350
How's your injury?

38:00.350 --> 38:02.500
Guan Huai is quick-tongued
only when he wants to live.

38:03.100 --> 38:04.700
You must have caught Fang Chang.

38:05.270 --> 38:06.870
He's now in the Nine-Square Maze Prison.

38:07.020 --> 38:07.950
He awaits your judgment.

38:09.790 --> 38:11.390
I knew you'd bring me good news.

38:11.950 --> 38:12.790
That's perfect.

38:13.430 --> 38:14.270
Hey, Simu.

38:15.910 --> 38:16.990
What exactly happened?

38:17.620 --> 38:18.620
How did you lose power

38:18.620 --> 38:19.660
and get wounded by him?

38:32.870 --> 38:33.790
I hate it most

38:33.790 --> 38:35.140
when someone wants to poke around.

38:37.580 --> 38:38.500
It's been 300 years.

38:39.310 --> 38:40.150
You're the Sovereign

38:40.390 --> 38:41.790
and I help you rule the Spirit World

38:41.790 --> 38:42.630
perfectly in sync.

38:43.050 --> 38:43.910
Do you and I

38:43.920 --> 38:45.280
have to be so precise about that?

38:48.750 --> 38:50.310
Do you have feelings for that general?

38:50.310 --> 38:51.150
Right Hand,

38:53.870 --> 38:54.910
you know very well

38:56.180 --> 38:57.140
that I am the Sovereign.

39:00.790 --> 39:01.630
Sorry, Your Grace.

39:03.060 --> 39:03.900
You should go back.

39:04.310 --> 39:05.150
Keep our world in order.

39:06.140 --> 39:07.180
When I'm back,

39:07.180 --> 39:08.020
don't let me down.

39:12.140 --> 39:12.980
Yes.

39:13.500 --> 39:14.430
I shall be there,

39:14.790 --> 39:16.140
awaiting your return.

39:16.860 --> 39:20.980
(Yiyuan Courtyard)

39:37.340 --> 39:41.100
(Liang)

39:42.350 --> 39:44.750
Evil spirits. Evil spirits everywhere.

39:44.990 --> 39:47.270
They eat people.

39:47.700 --> 39:50.100
They're evil spirits.

39:50.390 --> 39:51.310
They eat people.

39:51.310 --> 39:52.150
General Duan.

39:52.910 --> 39:54.140
Don't eat me.

39:54.140 --> 39:55.100
What's all this about?

39:55.660 --> 39:56.870
He's a mere swindler

39:56.870 --> 39:57.710
who fools people.

39:58.310 --> 40:00.100
He set up a stupid scam.

40:01.310 --> 40:02.830
And due to those baseless rumors,

40:03.140 --> 40:05.020
the one contributing greatly to our army

40:05.350 --> 40:06.270
was thrown into prison.

40:06.270 --> 40:07.110
Don't eat me.

40:09.660 --> 40:10.500
General Duan,

40:11.020 --> 40:12.750
there was a spirit in your army.

40:12.990 --> 40:14.020
Marshal Qin dealt with her

40:14.020 --> 40:14.860
and calmed your army.

40:15.100 --> 40:16.180
Instead of feeling thankful,

40:16.430 --> 40:17.660
you blame him now.

40:18.180 --> 40:19.020
Don't tell me

40:19.430 --> 40:20.790
you recruited that evil spirit.

40:20.950 --> 40:22.180
He Xiaoxiao colluded with evil,

40:22.180 --> 40:23.180
as everyone witnessed.

40:23.500 --> 40:24.470
She's still alive

40:25.140 --> 40:26.430
because Marshal Qin showed mercy.

40:26.580 --> 40:27.420
General Duan,

40:28.140 --> 40:29.500
don't you push it.

40:30.020 --> 40:31.020
How come I didn't know

40:31.620 --> 40:32.950
our soldiers

40:33.990 --> 40:34.830
should be judged

40:34.830 --> 40:36.020
by a swindler?

40:36.020 --> 40:37.200
Don't eat me. Spare me.

40:37.270 --> 40:38.390
Did someone deliberately

40:38.390 --> 40:39.310
disrupt our morale

40:40.100 --> 40:41.540
or did someone maliciously try

40:41.830 --> 40:43.350
to frame my capable strategist?

40:43.360 --> 40:44.200
You...

40:44.220 --> 40:47.870
Evil spirits. Spare me. Don't eat me.

40:48.470 --> 40:49.830
Now that it's a misunderstanding,

40:50.020 --> 40:51.350
then have this swindler

40:51.350 --> 40:52.210
taken away

40:52.220 --> 40:53.200
and have him beheaded.

40:53.200 --> 40:54.050
- Yes.
- Yes.

40:54.060 --> 40:55.120
Evil spirits.

40:55.270 --> 40:56.910
They eat people.

40:57.310 --> 40:58.620
So many evil spirits.

40:58.620 --> 41:01.620
They eat people.

41:01.750 --> 41:02.870
Evil spirits.

41:02.870 --> 41:03.710
General Duan,

41:04.060 --> 41:05.310
we'll have a major battle

41:05.310 --> 41:06.310
against Chong troops

41:06.500 --> 41:07.540
and we need talents.

41:07.950 --> 41:09.180
We must make concerted efforts

41:09.180 --> 41:10.020
to fight our enemies.

41:10.430 --> 41:11.950
Let's not blow our recovery plan

41:12.180 --> 41:13.660
over such trivial things.

41:25.870 --> 41:27.350
This is the information I collected

41:27.620 --> 41:28.470
as fast as possible

41:28.470 --> 41:29.310
on reaching Yunzhou,

41:29.750 --> 41:30.750
including city defense,

41:31.060 --> 41:32.180
garrison troops, formations,

41:32.540 --> 41:33.380
supplies, and weapons.

41:34.020 --> 41:34.910
Take a look, Marshal.

41:35.870 --> 41:37.220
Yunzhou is very far away

41:37.220 --> 41:38.100
in a messy situation.

41:38.470 --> 41:39.700
But you spied on the enemy

41:39.700 --> 41:40.700
and returned safely

41:40.700 --> 41:41.660
within only a few days.

41:41.830 --> 41:43.310
Impressive, indeed.

41:44.350 --> 41:45.190
Good job.

42:04.620 --> 42:05.500
Thank you, Miss.

42:23.470 --> 42:24.430
You gave all your salary

42:24.430 --> 42:25.470
to someone else.

42:26.100 --> 42:27.470
How will you survive this month?

42:29.100 --> 42:30.390
I spared no effort

42:30.390 --> 42:31.470
to predict the weather

42:31.700 --> 42:33.580
and I was even in prison because of you.

42:34.020 --> 42:34.950
With no compensation,

42:35.140 --> 42:36.390
won't I at least get a raise?

42:38.700 --> 42:39.540
Whatever you need

42:40.220 --> 42:41.100
should be offered.

42:46.060 --> 42:47.220
What did Miss Qiao say

42:47.700 --> 42:48.700
before she left?

42:50.750 --> 42:52.060
She's fully recovered.

42:52.620 --> 42:53.870
She'll return to her hometown

42:54.140 --> 42:55.060
for a peaceful life.

42:59.310 --> 43:00.350
Your Grace, what does

43:00.500 --> 43:01.430
your hometown look like?

43:02.390 --> 43:03.270
I'd like to visit it.

43:08.390 --> 43:09.950
When dead trees blossom,

43:10.500 --> 43:11.540
I'll grant your wish.

43:21.240 --> 43:26.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

43:26.900 --> 43:31.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

43:32.510 --> 43:37.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

43:38.180 --> 43:42.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

43:43.870 --> 43:45.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

43:57.920 --> 44:03.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

44:03.540 --> 44:07.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

44:09.240 --> 44:14.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

44:14.860 --> 44:18.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

44:20.570 --> 44:22.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

44:25.120 --> 44:28.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

44:28.280 --> 44:30.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

44:30.810 --> 44:36.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

44:36.330 --> 44:39.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

44:39.570 --> 44:44.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

44:44.770 --> 44:47.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

44:47.790 --> 44:50.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

44:50.870 --> 44:53.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

44:53.400 --> 44:58.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

44:58.990 --> 45:02.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

45:02.220 --> 45:07.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

45:07.330 --> 45:10.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
